{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>根據「鏡週刊」報導，朱軒洋已搬離先前與前女友同居的生活圈，現居台北市內湖區一帶，與吳卓源的活動範圍相近；而吳卓源也被指選擇在同區域內更換住所，現居於一處外觀較為老舊的大廈，兩人被爆舊情復燃。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20241002/918197032542801920879526.jpeg/s3a2VgW5R7YJ5PDAyk1k2IZXEGBNaGNId2qbrndqm64\" alt=\"吳卓源Julia（IG@juliawu94）\"><figcaption>吳卓源Julia（IG@juliawu94）</figcaption></figure><p>更多吳卓源Julia的相片：</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123566712352935936846519.jpeg/ySFkuhId0ttCph33ULwYAKwHtMqKCFDmUt4ZelLeGXo\" alt=\"吳卓源Julia（IG@juliawu94）\"><figcaption>吳卓源Julia（IG@juliawu94）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20241002/918197032630882304803641.jpeg/e2IogQnHGzHuAXpZJKjTRpKU_8DEB3adpS4QmKUuEJg\" alt=\"吳卓源Julia（IG@juliawu94）\"><figcaption>吳卓源Julia（IG@juliawu94）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20241002/918197032861569024267143.jpeg/-I_iROUENeTKiCCmVnDnNFh9rv3pn932w5BOyMOQTsg\" alt=\"吳卓源Julia（IG@juliawu94）\"><figcaption>吳卓源Julia（IG@juliawu94）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20241002/918197033029210112102874.jpeg/_5NcwPZm89SJBR8ExyQpNXJDo6vBcSwoEiFh9hIhYfY\" alt=\"吳卓源Julia（IG@juliawu94）\"><figcaption>吳卓源Julia（IG@juliawu94）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20241002/918197034132443136490358.jpeg/w3cfXLSJA7nuE5gQ_bTHb9ltQ2TMKfEG_W08cP1tPHA\" alt=\"吳卓源Julia（IG@juliawu94）\"><figcaption>吳卓源Julia（IG@juliawu94）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20241002/918197034870640640495108.jpeg/JdG8ch6K2lVPYPzpaa5_vYVY2yMGM53RHYqbGx2Kmxs\" alt=\"吳卓源Julia（IG@juliawu94）\"><figcaption>吳卓源Julia（IG@juliawu94）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20241002/918197035181019136092764.jpeg/3RQFCuy5QSZlTpqOgbWZiKeK-VNfHKcZYoPK92KDyvc\" alt=\"吳卓源Julia（IG@juliawu94）\"><figcaption>吳卓源Julia（IG@juliawu94）</figcaption><